<title>SRI LANKA: Sri Lanka Ceylon Glass posts year profit.</title>
<headline>Sri Lanka Ceylon Glass posts year profit.</headline>
<dateline>COLOMBO 1996-08-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Audited results of Ceylon Glass Company for the 1995/1996 financial year.</p>
<p>(in millions of rupees unless stated):</p>
<p>			    1995/96		1994/95</p>
<p>    Turnover	     655.44    vs	 456.55</p>
<p>    Net profit	    81.22    vs (loss) 82.30</p>
<p>    Tax			---     vs	    --</p>
<p>NOTE - Ceylon Glass Company is Sri Lanka's monopoly glass bottle manufacturer. Company profits in the financial year to March 31, 1996 are not taxed due to cumulative losses in the two previous financial years, a company spokesman said.</p>
<p>-- Colombo newsroom tel 941-434319</p>
</text>
